headline.main: U.S. COMMAND CAR RUNS INTO MINE FIELD; Driver Discovers Plight in Nick of Time and Backs Out

lead_paragraph: WITH THE UNITED STATES ARMY NORTHEAST OF BEJA, Tunisia, April 28 (Delayed) (AP) -- A big command car was speeding along a dirt road ahead of American infantry moving up through the fields when it suddenly came to a halt.
abstract: incident of US command car in Ger mine field described
